<br>
People from Tunare tryed to bring the Tunare way with them, but it failed, so most people from Tunare adopted to the ways they saw this server was going to be. Aleal wanted me to join CS with him, I told him that I didnt want to becuase I saw the CS way was the anti Tunare way (my god on their website it states that if you are in a group with non guildmates and a guildmate wants a group, then you should kick the non guildmate out of the group so you have room for the guildy - thats just sad!)<br>
